.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Food: strawberry, lime, potato, pomegranate, peach
Cigar: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
Sport: skiing, cycling, surfing, handball, golf
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Food:strawberry == Color:red
2. Food:lime == Pet:dog
3. Sport:skiing == Color:green
4. Food:potato == Sport:cycling
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Cigar:old-gold == Pet:snails
7. Cigar:kools == Color:yellow
8. Sport:surfing is in the middle
9. Food:pomegranate is on the far left
10. Cigar:chesterfields is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Cigar:kools is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Cigar:lucky-strike == Sport:handball
13. Food:peach == Cigar:parliaments
14. Food:pomegranate is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
